import React from 'react';
import { Inputs, Form, InlineForm, InputSeparator, Button, DefaultInput } from "../form/inputs";


const ContactUsForm = () => {
    return(
        <>
        <Form>
        <DefaultInput
          label="From?"
          placeholder="Enter pickup location"
          id="location"
        />
        <DefaultInput
          label="Where to?"
          placeholder="Enter drop off for estimate"
          id="dropoff"
        />
        <InlineForm>
          <Inputs
            label="When?"
            placeholder="Today"
            id="date"
          />
          <InputSeparator>
            <Inputs label="Time?" placeholder="06:45 AM" id="time" />
          </InputSeparator>
        </InlineForm>
        <Button>Request Now</Button>
      </Form>
        </>
    );
}

export default ContactUsForm;
